  "overview": {
    "summary": "Blobert Goopington is a Plasmoid who was artificially created by Dr. Nikolas. They are an Artificer prior to their first death, where they ate an Edelith Pod. they returned by a patron named Liorah who deems humanity worthless and wants to find a reason of which they deserve any inherent value, through Blobert, who is inherently childish and curious about everything, he seems to be the perfect window to humans.",
    "personality": "Blobert is clueless and unintelligent at times but shows genuine care, and naive recklessness towards things he cares about. He is impulsive but can be very understanding at times. He is book smart by information hoarding rather than genuine understanding of the materials.",
    "likes":    ["Trying new things", "Edelith pods", "his friends", "Blobbing"],
    "dislikes": ["Alchemy jugs"],
    "trivia": [
      { "text": "Blobert does not posess Luminessence", "redacted": false },
      { "text": "He seems to be the only character that has been resurrected.", "redacted": false },
      { "redacted": true },
      { "redacted": true }
    ],
    "sideQuote": "My plan was to drown herb to scare the kids."
  },

